{"tid":1847752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［民間組織力］若果無2019既示威，今次民間抗疫抗爭一定無組織得咁快咁強！","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:51:26.000Z","uid":219007,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6ac34a77d9301f3a7946cf4af829db3a3c7c7f","tid":1847752,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"粉嶺一有事即有火魔法<br />\n<br />\n醫護間工業行動八方即有支援<br />\n<br />\n封關民意一星期已經章顯<br />\n<br />\n如果2019無呢埸運動出現<br />\n<br />\n今次肯定要慢慢組織，組織力肯定慢依家幾倍<br />\n<br />\n學前幾日梁錦祥話齋<br />\n<br />\n靜係週街中國人肯定一早已經大爆法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76719f11fbed2ce79e36ee5c588547c8ef37b980","tid":1847752,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369ec80b04199a7e849dbdc512cdcc5159dc2bb0","tid":1847752,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:45:56.000Z","msg":"粉嶺接近核爆級別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf02df36c52b9759392c7c52a78613b24b492894","tid":1847752,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0334ecdbd7a17a4ae83a22ec3334dd97fd3250e6","tid":1847752,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"反送中示威救港"},{"pid":"bb9403a291d54e2929a8dd0b773e233e3e823130","tid":1847752,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253cd1a43103f397cf1a9ea6fd32079b3bad1a7c","tid":1847752,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思阻大家少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但事關重大，請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懇求大家盡快無限期三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"770eed3d095a3ea2816e73f62966a456d1f40286","tid":1847752,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"你岩"}]}